title: Looney Tunes Golden Collection (Vol. 1-6) files named for tvdb x
description:
This is the content from xxMaestroxx's torrent, but repackaged so that a media server (e.g., xbmc, plex) can pull the metadata from online sources (e.g., thetvdb.com)

The DVD file structure has been eliminated and replaced with one that matches the original episode air date e.g.,

/looney tunes
  /season 1930
    /looney tunes - s1930e02 - Congo Jazz.avi
    /looney tunes - s1930e04 - The Booze Hangs High.avi
  /season 1931
    /looney tunes - s1931e09 - Smile Darn Ya, Smile!.avi
    /looney tunes - s1931e11 - One More Time.avi
